    • requestUpdate

      private void requestUpdate​(long delay)
      We use the provided delay before refreshing the content of the preview. If further modification is brought to the layout before expiration of it we restart the timer. The idea is to lower the resources used to refresh the preview window content. The delay is expressed in milliseconds. In some cases it is wise to used delay = 0, e.g. when opening the window.
